&lt;li&gt;Generating ideas for new investment insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply a variety of skills and techniques in finance, data science and statistics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with our technology, portfolio management and investment process teams to deliver exceptional investment performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Domain Expertise&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;– You have a deep understanding of the drivers of business success, securities valuation, and markets. You can effectively apply both creativity and discipline to sourcing and evaluating novel data sets that are useful for predicting the performance of companies and securities.&lt;/li&gt;
